 desc' when attempting to retrieve ads from the adservice. It suggests a problem within the adservice that is causing the frontend to fail in retrieving ads.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Repeated log entries from frontend services noting 'failed to get ads: rpc error: code = Unknown desc ='.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"adservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"Multiple logs with the occurrence of 'Exception in thread \\\"grpc-default-executor' and 'java.lang.Error: Injected error' indicate possible internal errors being injected in the adservice's getRandomAds method.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Log entries mentioning 'Exception in thread \\\"grpc-default-executor' and 'AdService-getRandomAds-exception'.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"adservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"Logs show triggers and installation of rules for handling exceptions in AdService's getRandomAds method. This may point to intentional error injection or testing within the service.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Log mention of 'RuleTriggerMethodAdapter.injectTriggerPoint' and 'org.jboss.byteman.agent.Transformer'.\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```", "metric_analysis_findings": "根据我们获取到的异常指标数据，以下是初步扫描阶段对故障现象的分析结果：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_metric_keys\": [\"rrt_max\", \"pod_cpu_usage\", \"node_memory_usage_rate\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"cartservice-1\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max指标显示故障期间响应时间显著增加，可能由其服务依赖或Pod资源问题导致。\",\n      \"evidence\": \"rrt_max指标的fault_median为7057.0，与normal_median的变化率为1.422，显著异常。\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"redis-cart-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"Pod资源异常，pod_cpu_usage指标在故障期间明显升高，占CPU资源使用的变化超出正常范围。\",\n      \"evidence\": \"pod_cpu_usage的fault_p99为0.08，与normal_p99相比变化率为1.2299。\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"aiops-k8s-04\",\n      \"reason\": \"Node的node_memory_usage_rate异常，可能导致运行在此节点上的Pod性能问题。\",\n      \"evidence\": \"node_memory_usage_rate在故障期间fault_median下降为26.32，与正常值变化率为0.3848，可能间接影响了相关服务。\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n上述分析汇总了故障期间的显著异常调用链和初步假设，下一步需要确认异常的根本原因并深入关联分析。", "trace_analysis_findings": "以下是对调用链数据的初步分析，发现了多个显著异常的调用链和相关原因。以下是分析概述：\n\n### JSON 输出\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_trace_keys\": [\n    \"latency_spike\",\n    \"frontend->cartservice\",\n    \"checkoutservice->paymentservice\",\n    \"redis->cartservice\",\n    \"emailservice->checkoutservice\",\n    \"recommendationservice->frontend\",\n    \"recommendationservice->productcatalog\",\n    \"shippingservice->checkoutservice\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend->cartservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"前端服务调用购物车服务时显著延迟，延迟倍数为 7.4。\",\n      \"evidence\": \"正常平均耗时 3694.50 ms；异常时耗时高达 27629.5 ms。异常发生 2 次。\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"checkoutservice->paymentservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"结账服务调用支付服务时显著延迟，延迟倍数为 5.7。\",\n      \"evidence\": \"正常平均耗时 12831.39 ms；异常时耗时高达 73029.0 ms。异常发生 1 次。\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"redis->cartservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"购物车服务操作 Redis 时大幅延迟，延迟倍数达 12.5。\",\n      \"evidence\": \"正常平均耗时 1361.25 ms；异常时耗时高达 10189.007 ms。异常发生 2 次。\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"emailservice->checkoutservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"结账服务调用邮件服务延迟加倍。\",\n      \"evidence\": \"正常平均耗时 699.97 ms；异常时耗时 1491.75 ms。异常发生 2 次。\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"recommendationservice->frontend\",\n      \"reason\": \"前端服务调用推荐服务时延迟提升。\",\n      \"evidence\": \"正常平均耗时 3855.62 ms；异常时耗时 5012.14 ms。异常发生 2 次。\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"recommendationservice->productcatalog\",\n      \"reason\": \"推荐服务调用产品目录时延迟。\",\n      \"evidence\": \"正常平均耗时 2975.89 ms；异常时耗时 3228.44 ms。异常发生 6 次。\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"shippingservice->checkoutservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"结账服务调用物流服务时延迟增加。\",\n      \"evidence\": \"正常平均耗时 225.57 ms；异常时耗时 786.0 ms。异常发生 2 次。\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n### 初步结论\n1. **性能瓶颈**：\n   - **Redis 服务高延迟**对购物车服务的影响显著。\n   - **支付服务**调用时表现出紧张的延迟，可能是支付网关或数据库问题。\n\n2. **错误传播路径**：\n   - 核心传播路径